<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Glamorgan</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Established in 1958, Glamorgan in South West Calgary, Alberta is a warm and welcoming residential community that is bound by the Sarcee Trail on the west, the Glenmore Trail on the South, 37 Street W on the east and the Richmond Road on the north. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Represented by the Ward 6 councilor in the Calgary City Council, Glamorgan houses approximately 6500 people living across in a variety of dwellings.</p>
            <p class="par-lg">Located at a convenient 10-minute drive from Downtown Calgary, the Glamorgan real estate is well connected with a strategically planned network of pathways and streets. </p>
        </div>
